Comment: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================NEXT====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}骗人的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果春日是个变态呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}难道说仲村… 把体操服的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想更了解春日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快就来找她做爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好好珍惜彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}佐伯是天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对着镜子好好看看你自己
